'''Brian''' is a shop owner who runs [[Brian's Battleaxe Bazaar]] in [[Port Sarim]]. He sells [[battleaxe]]s, from [[Bronze battleaxe|bronze]] to [[Adamant battleaxe|adamant]]. He also plays a small role in the [[One Small Favour]] [[Quests|quest]], agreeing to sharpen the [[jungle forester]]'s axe if his friend is returned to him.

